installation:
The product can be installed in different varieties, in respect with the Declaration of Performance (DoP):
• Installation in a rigid wall and floor;
• Installation in flexible wall (metal stud gypsum plasterboard wall);
• Installation in flexible wall (metal stud gypsum plasterboard wall), sealing with gypsum;
• Installation in flexible wall (metal stud gypsum plasterboard wall), sealing with mortar;
• Installation in shaft wall, sealing with gypsum;
• Installation in shaft wall, sealing with rigid rock wool boards with coating;
• Installation in shaft wall with IFW installation kit and plaster joint filler;
• Installation in flexible and rigid wall, sealing with rigid rock wool boards with coating;
• Installation in rigid floor, sealing with rigid rock wool boards with coating;
• Installation remote from the wall, sealing and insulation with rigid rock wool boards with coating;
• Installation remote from the wall + GEOFLAM plates (threaded rods and U-shaped steel profiles).

Because of the different ways of installation, the product is declared as 'as produced'' in this EPD.

Consequently, regarding installation, this EPD only includes the environmental impact related to the product itself (i.e. treatment of the waste arising from the packaging of the final product). The impact of possible additional products and materials, necessary for the installation of the product, is not included in this EPD. However, this impact shall be taken into account at building level.

More detailed information on the different installation scenarios can be found in the chapter "Additional technical information for scenario development" in this EPD.
